      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'm not really sure what you mean by \"memory goblins\"? i'm just looking for technical debugging steps. specifically for an embedded system where i might not be able to run heavy tools like Valgrind. what are some lighter weight ways to track allocations in real-time?",
